Event.info: OSINT - GandCrab Version 3 Released With Autorun Feature and Desktop Background

Attribute.value:
GandCrab version 3 was released earlier this week with a few noticeable changes. The most noticeable change is the addition of a desktop background.

Unfortunately, at this time GandCrab 3 cannot be decrypted for free.
